<h2>Don&apos;t Start from Scratch. Grab a Module in the Puppet Forge.</h2>
<p>Modules are reusable, sharable units of Puppet code. They can automate tasks such as setting up a database, web server, or mail server. There are over 100 modules ready for use in the Puppet Module Forge.</p>
